summary:
Beatriz Aguiar is a very creative studio artist.
She has build up, during her career, a strong knowledge in the leather design.
Originally singer-songwriter she has participated in some of the most important music events around the world. 
For several years she has been creating in different artistic directions. 
Beatriz’s passion for art has always been her drive in life.
In 2010 she has created her own brand of leather handbags, Beabz Amsterdam.
Original designs, daring and innovative in the European market.
Her interest in experimenting with materials and colors, creating very original effects, makes her work unique and creative. After 5 collections, Beabz remains extremely personal, where the detailed craftsmanship is a  trademark, and a strong feature in her designs.  

Experience: Production and manufacturing.								                			
Concept creator in Europe and South America. 									
Responsible for the development of the collection.								
Inspiration board – presentation. Colors, forms and materials and accessories choice.	Textil design	. Graphic presentation. Marketing and promotion.
Founder of Make The Match Agency - for Music Consultancy and International Promotion.
Currently Beatriz Aguiar works for Proma Foundation in the production of the Colombia Music and Arts Festival - ColorEs Colombia.
